  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Closed shop block to be handed over to Samurthi beneficiaries - protest at Pattanai junction",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today, a protest action was taken at the place on the demand that it should be revealed immediately who set up the shop complex located at Pathanai junction on Kotakalai - Thalawakalai road and that the said shop complex was started in the year 2015 for Samurthi beneficiaries.",
        "Samurthi beneficiaries and the people of the area in support of them participated in this protest and expressed their opposition. The people who participated in this protest led by Subramaniam Raja, People's Liberation Front member of Kotakalai Pradeshiya Sabha, have set up a shop block in our area without our knowledge. An article with full details was published in some media in this regard.",
        "After that it was revealed that it was started for public use. So it is clear that this place is occupied by individuals. We want to provide this to the people. They told us that we cannot travel to Talawakkala to avail Samurthi services.",
        "Many scandals have taken place behind the construction of this building. Although I have been questioning this for the last two years, Kotakalai Pradeshiya Sabha director has not given me proper answers. He says he has nothing to do with this building. He says it was set up in 2008 by the nearby temple management council. This temple does not have such an administrative council. Because I belong to this area. How can a building be constructed in 2022 for permission granted in 2008? How was the Pradeshiya Sabha administration watching a building come up in an area within its jurisdiction? The plot behind this should be revealed. It belongs to the people. He said that if we do not get proper answers, our struggle will continue.",
        "Kotakalai Pradeshiya Sabha was started in the year 2018. In the year 2008, Nuwara Eliya Pradeshiya Sabha has granted permission to construct the building to the said temple administration. It may have been built now due to lack of funds at that time. We have not given permission to anyone in this building. No one takes permission from us. Answers have been given to all those who have raised oral and written questions regarding this. But the building has been erected as per permission given by Nuwara Eliya Pradeshiya Sabha. We have questioned the temple administration about this. They have submitted the relevant documents. He said that we have requested to renew this scheme."
      ],
